<br>
&quot;What's the problem here&quot;, demanded Hermes.  &quot;Do you know this bickering amongst the Pantheon has spread amongst the mortals as well?&quot;<br>
<br>
::I have just returned from Hades realm where I have just delivered the next batch of souls.  The majority of them died fighting over who deserves this temple.  It seems there's a Holy war erupting on earth.<br>
<br>
Hermes pointed his staff in front of him, and a swirling mist appeared.  In it, was shone the events that are occurring on earth.<br>
<br>
::Here's the battlefield right outside Rome, and here's the outcome in Thebes.  Both sides have taken heavy losses.  If I didn't know better, I would think brother Ares was involved.<br>
